title: Case Was Received
body: On March 8, 2021, we received your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190124000, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
